  "2026-07-06T22:23:28.812Z",codex,"Creation evidence: live pm --help --json lists test-runs-worker as a top-level subcommand with description 'Internal background worker command'; pm contracts --flags-only --json also includes it in the command list. pm search --status all for test-runs-worker/internal worker/help surface found no focused open item; existing hits were broad/closed help or coverage work. This item keeps the worker reachable for orchestration but removes it from the default agent-facing command budget."
